                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This feature enhancement is not compatible with the Table Data Gateway pattern.\n\nThe solution when writing special queries is to write a Select query:\n\n{code}\n$table = new MyTable();\n\n$select = $table->getAdapter()->select();\n$select->group(...);\n$select->having(...);\n$stmt = $select->query();\n{code}",
